tool_description: A Configurable HTML Template Generator with 4 different templates.
name: HTML Template Generator
title: HTML Template Generator

api_list.name: HTML TEMPLATE 1(CUSTOM)
api_list.description: This is the custom template, you can do almost anything with this template and have it turn out great!
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://html-template-generator.p.rapidapi.com/template/1"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "html-template-generator.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
